Sentencas: In this research, La0.7Sr0.3Fe0.7Ga0.3O3-delta (LSFG) perovskite oxide was successfully prepared using a microwave-assisted combustion method, and employed as both anode and cathode in symmetrical solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: La0.7Sr0.3Fe0.7Ga0.3O3-δ as electrode material for a symmetrical solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A maximumpower density of 489 mW cm(-2) was achieved at 800 degrees C with wet H-2 as the fuel and ambient air as the oxidant in a single cell with the configuration LSFG vertical bar La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta vertical bar LSFG.
Titulo: La0.7Sr0.3Fe0.7Ga0.3O3-δ as electrode material for a symmetrical solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Furthermore, the cells demonstrated good stability in H-2 and acceptable sulfur tolerance.
Titulo: La0.7Sr0.3Fe0.7Ga0.3O3-δ as electrode material for a symmetrical solid oxide fuel cell
